      "writtenOn": "2026-03-12T10:23:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If tracking FIN-WAIT states, we will need to account that either initiator or responder could start the connection tear-down (i.e. we cannot assume that initiator will start connection tear-down) and track states on either side accordingly.\n\nAlso, there is still a possibility that simultaneous close scenario will occur (i.e initiator and responder both send a FIN a the same time).",
      "revId": "d557b77cccaeb86874074e3aac37a11c8a6a996a",
